MAX_PLAYER_NAME.description: A value which defines the maximum length of a player's name, 24 characters by default.

MAX_PLAYERS.description: A value which defines the number of players that can join the server. It is separate from the 'maxplayers' server variable.

MAX_VEHICLES.description: A value which defines the maximum number of vehicles and equals 2000.

MAX_ACTORS.description: A value which defines the maximum number of actors and equals 1000.

INVALID_PLAYER_ID.description: A value which defines an invalid player's id and equals 0xFFFF.

INVALID_VEHICLE_ID.description: A value which defines an invalid vehicle's id and equals 0xFFFF.

INVALID_ACTOR_ID.description: A value which defines an invalid actor's id and equals 0xFFFF.

NO_TEAM.description: A value used to tag players as not beloning to any team and equals 255.

MAX_OBJECTS.description: A value which defines the maximum number of objects and equals 1000.

INVALID_OBJECT_ID.description: A value which defines an invalid object's id and equals 0xFFFF.

MAX_GANG_ZONES.description: A value which defines the maximum number of gang zones and equals 1024.

MAX_PLAYER_TEXT_DRAWS.description: A value which defines the maximum number of textdraws and equals 2048.

MAX_MENUS.description: A value which defines the maximum number of menus and equals 128.

MAX_3DTEXT_GLOBAL.description: A value which defines the maximum number of global 3D text labels and equals 1024.

MAX_3DTEXT_PLAYER.description: A value which defines the maximum number of player 3D text labels and equals 1024.

MAX_PICKUPS.description: A value which defines the maximum number of pickups and equals 4096.

INVALID_MENU.description: A value which defines an invalid menu's id and equals 0xFF.

INVALID_TEXT_DRAW.description: A value which defines an invalid textdraw's id and equals 0xFFFF.

INVALID_GANG_ZONE.description: A value which defines an invalid gang zone's id and equals -1.

INVALID_3DTEXT_ID.description: A value which defines an invalid 3D text label's id and equals 0xFFFF.

PLAYER_STATE_ONFOOT.description: A value which defines the player' state when being on foot, it has the id 1.

PLAYER_STATE_NONE.description: A value which defines the player' state when being initialized, it has the id 0.

PLAYER_STATE_DRIVER.description: A value which defines the player' state when driving a vehicle, it has the id 2.

PLAYER_STATE_PASSENGER.description: A value which defines the player' state when being a passenger of a vehicle, it has the id 3.

PLAYER_STATE_EXIT_VEHICLE.description: A value which defines the player' state when exiting a vehicle, it has the id 4.

PLAYER_STATE_ENTER_VEHICLE_DRIVER.description: A value which defines the player' state when entering a vehicle as a driver, it has the id 5.

PLAYER_STATE_ENTER_VEHICLE_PASSENGER.description: A value which defines the player' state when entering a vehicle as a passenger, it has the id 6.

PLAYER_STATE_WASTED.description: A value which defines the player' state when dead or on class selection, it has the id 7.

PLAYER_STATE_SPAWNED.description: A value which defines the player' state when spawned, it has the id 8.

PLAYER_STATE_SPECTATING.description: A value which defines the player' state when spectating, it has the id 9.

PLAYER_MARKERS_MODE_OFF.description: A value which defines the state of the player's marker as being off, it has the id 0.

PLAYER_MARKERS_MODE_GLOBAL.description: A value which defines the state of the player's marker as being globaly visible, it has the id 1.

PLAYER_MARKERS_MODE_STREAMED.description: A value which defines the state of the player's marker as being visible for streamed players, it has the id 2.

CLICK_SOURCE_SCOREBOARD.description: A value which defines the source of the player's click to be the score board (ID 0).

EDIT_RESPONSE_CANCEL.description: A value which defines the object edition cancellation response type (ID 0).

EDIT_RESPONSE_FINAL.description: A value which defines the object edition save response type (ID 1).

EDIT_RESPONSE_UPDATE.description: A value which defines the object edition update response type (ID 2).

SELECT_OBJECT_GLOBAL_OBJECT.description: A value which defines the object selection type to be of a global object.

SELECT_OBJECT_PLAYER_OBJECT.description: A value which defines the object selection type to be of a player object.

BULLET_HIT_TYPE_NONE.description: A value which defines the type of the target that was hit by the shot to be nothing (Used with OnPlayerWeaponShot), (ID 0).

BULLET_HIT_TYPE_PLAYER.description: A value which defines the type of the target that was hit by the shot to be another player (Used with OnPlayerWeaponShot), (ID 1).

BULLET_HIT_TYPE_VEHICLE.description: A value which defines the type of the target that was hit by the shot to be a vehicle (Used with OnPlayerWeaponShot), (ID 2).

BULLET_HIT_TYPE_OBJECT.description: A value which defines the type of the target that was hit by the shot to be an object (Used with OnPlayerWeaponShot), (ID 3).

BULLET_HIT_TYPE_PLAYER_OBJECT.description: A value which defines the type of the target that was hit by the shot to be a player object (Used with OnPlayerWeaponShot), (ID 4).
